These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, western, documentary, fantasy
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
5. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | western | fantasy | documentary |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, social-worker, project-manager, entrepreneur
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the analyst is on the left of the project-manager##1
3. the project-manager is in an odd position##4
4. the analyst is the person watching crime movies##1
5. the social-worker is on the right of the project-manager##1
6. the analyst is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Job   | entrepreneur    | analyst | project-manager | social-worker    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
House: townhouse, wooden, cape-cod, ranch-style
1. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
4. the ranch-style house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the townhouse house is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| House   | cape-cod        | ranch-style     | townhouse | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, aconite, balloon-flower
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, indie, reggae
1. the person who growsamaryllis is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower         | balloon-flower | sunflower | amaryllis | aconite |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | blues   | folk    | reggae  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, hip-hop, jazz, punk
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, fuchsia, chestnut, mauve
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is the fan of punk##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the fan of folk##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes black is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | folk    | jazz   | punk       |
| Color   | black | mauve | chestnut | fuchsia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, epic, time-travel
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, indie, folk, dubstep
1. the fan of indie is in an even position##4
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
3. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | documentary | time-travel | animation |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | indie     | electronic  | folk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, game, dunhill, swisher
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, roller, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
4. the person driving the ship is the bongani-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | bongani | swisher | dunhill | game    |
| Transport     | ship | roller  | car     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
House: townhouse, colonial, art-deco, cape-cod
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the colonial house##3
2. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the townhouse house is between the cape-cod house and the colonial house##2
6. the owner of the fish is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the fish is between the townhouse house and the owner of the goat##2
8. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the colonial house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| House   | colonial | townhouse      | cape-cod | art-deco |
| Pet   | bird  | guinea-pig | fish    | goat            |

