.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, mango, pepper, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, writing, reading, board-games
1. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person eating pepper##2
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating pepper is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | watermelon | mango   | cabbage | pepper |
| Hobby    | board-games     | writing | filmmaking     | reading  |

