.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, juice, soy-milk
House: art-deco, palace, victorian, craftsman
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the craftsman house##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the craftsman house is between the art-deco house and the person drinking juice##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the palace house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| House   | victorian | palace | craftsman        | art-deco    |

