.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, tea, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, software-developer, dressmaker, teacher
1. the project-manager is in an even position##4
2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the teacher##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta   | water   | juice      | tea      |
| Job      | software-developer | dressmaker | teacher | project-manager |

