.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, carrot, cherry, lemon
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, frog, hamster
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
3. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
4. the person eating cabbage is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cherry is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | lemon | carrot  | cherry  | cabbage |
| Pet   | hamster  | frog | cat | ferret   |

