3. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
4. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
5. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water | almond-milk | 7up  |
| Transport     | boat   | bike  | train  | motorbike |

