.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, superhero, western
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, havana, ritmeester, cain
1. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching family movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching western movies is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | family | martial-arts |
| Cigar           | cain     | chaman     | ritmeester   | havana         |

