.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, snowmobile, bike
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skateboarding, soccer, weightlifting
1. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person driving the jet-ski##2
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Transport   | bike | jet-ski         | roller   | snowmobile |
| Sport   | soccer    | skateboarding | weightlifting | ice-hockey   |

