.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, camping, video-games, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
3. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | water | 7up    | milk       | fanta |
| Hobby       | camping  | video-games | drawing | collecting  |

