.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, indonesian, pakistani
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, punk, blues, electronic
1. the american is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the fan of punk is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the american is on the right of the fan of blues##1
6. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | american  | pakistani |
| Music-Genre     | gospel      | blues       | punk | electronic     |

